message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.NEURON - This paper involves the use of deep learning for image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the application of this technique is in the medical field (cs.MED) specifically for the analysis of animal cross section images. The use of deep learning for medical image analysis is also a topic in neuroscience (cs.NEURON).
